# How to run

You can either go to [Playground Link](https://www.typescriptlang.org/play/?#code/GYVwdgxgLglg9mABDAzgfQDYFMDmMBG2AFGAFyJggC2+WATgJTn5xzYCGSA3gFCL-) or if you have personal computer:

1. Clone this repo.
2. Navigate your terminal to the file.
3. Make sure you have installed [Node](https://nodejs.org/en).
3. Run `npx tsx index.ts`

---

To change the input, go to line 39 and change the number.

Peace.
